/blog/agra-mathura-vrindavan-one-day-trip     /blog/agra-mathura-vrindavan-one-day-trip/               301

# Blog 200 rewrites for nested paths
/blog/taj-mahal-visiting-guide/*              /blog/taj-mahal-visiting-guide/index.html                200
/blog/best-time-to-visit-taj-mahal/*          /blog/best-time-to-visit-taj-mahal/index.html            200
/blog/agra-one-day-sightseeing/*              /blog/agra-one-day-sightseeing/index.html                200
